description: The country returns to stricter coronavirus restrictions on Christmas Eve until at least 12 January.
title: Covid-19: Irish government authorises Pfizer-BioNTech vaccine
title_page: Covid-19: Irish government authorises Pfizer-BioNTech vaccine - BBC News
maintext: Professor Philip Nolan said he does not think the measures being introduced will be enough to bring the virus under control and this time it is coming "really fast and really hard" and the next few days will determine what happens in January.
